The '''silver antz''' (sing. '''silver ant''') were a [[Sentience/Legends|semi-sentient]] variety of the [[Ant/Legends|antz]] native to [[Kubindi/Legends|Kubindi]]. They were bipedal, warlike insectoids who traveled through forests to gather food in [[Army/Legends|armies]].

